         <abstract>
            <p>Christian version of <title ref="LIT1915Mashaf"/>). The work, belonging to the magical and apocryphal literature, contains the revelation and teaching of the secret names of Jesus and his twelve apostles, who are able to perfomr miracles thanks to these names. It exists in two principal versions, a short one (<title ref="LIT3943ArdeetChS"/>) and a long one (<title ref="LIT3944ArdeetChL"/>). 
It is not known whether the work is a translation or an original composition.
            </p>
